        these Terms and to our
        <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>,
        <a href="/community-guidelines/">Community Guidelines</a>, and
        <a href="/safety/">Safety Tips</a>.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>If you don’t agree to these Terms, do not use Luvmood.</strong>
      </p>

      <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You must be at least <strong>18 years old</strong>.</li>
        <li>You must be legally able to enter into a binding contract under the laws of your jurisdiction.</li>
        <li>You must not have been previously banned from the Service.</li>
        <li>You must not be a registered sex offender of any kind.</li>
        <li>You must not be subject to any sanctions list maintained by the United States or your country of residence.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We may verify your age and identity at any time, and we may remove or
        suspend accounts that misrepresent these details.
      </p>

