        <li>Keep your login credentials secure. You’re responsible for activity on your account.</li>
        <li>You can delete your account at any time from <strong>Settings → Account → Delete account</strong>.</li>
        <li>We may suspend or terminate your account if you violate these Terms, our Community Guidelines, or applicable law.</li>
      </ul>

