      <p>You agree <strong>not</strong> to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Harass, threaten, stalk, bully, intimidate, or harm any user.</li>
        <li>Post nudity, sexually explicit content, or any content sexualising or involving minors.</li>
        <li>Send unsolicited sexual content or pressure other users for such content.</li>
        <li>Spam, defraud, scam, phish, or solicit money, gifts, or financial information from other users.</li>
        <li>Promote, sell, or solicit prostitution, escort services, or other commercial sexual services.</li>
        <li>Use the Service for any commercial purpose, including advertising, recruiting, or surveying, without our written permission.</li>
        <li>Post content that is hateful, discriminatory, or promotes violence against people based on race, ethnicity, national origin, religion, sexual orientation, gender identity, disability, or any protected class.</li>
        <li>Share, distribute, or post other people’s private information (doxxing).</li>
        <li>Use automated tools (bots, scrapers, crawlers) to access, copy, or interact with the Service.</li>
        <li>Reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to extract source code from the app.</li>
        <li>Attempt to circumvent moderation, blocking, age verification, banning, or any other safety system.</li>
        <li>Create accounts after being banned, or help banned users do so.</li>
        <li>Interfere with, overload, or attempt to disrupt the Service or any other user’s use of it.</li>
        <li>Violate any applicable law or regulation.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We use both automated systems and human review to enforce these
        rules. Violations can result in content removal, feature
        restrictions, account suspension, or permanent banning without
        refund. See our <a href="/community-guidelines/">Community Guidelines</a> for more detail.
