      </p>

      <p><strong>Auto-renewing subscriptions (Premium).</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>If you purchase a subscription, it will <strong>automatically renew</strong> at the end of each billing period at the then-current price unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the period ends.</li>
        <li>You can manage and cancel subscriptions in your Apple ID or Google Play account settings — not in the Luvmood app.</li>
        <li>The subscription duration and price are shown to you at the point of purchase, and again in your Platform receipt.</li>
        <li>Unused portions of a free trial (if any) are forfeited when you purchase a subscription.</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Coins.</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Coins are a limited, revocable licence to use in-app features (chat requests, gifts, boosts). They are <strong>not</strong> property, currency, or a stored-value instrument.</li>
        <li>Coins have <strong>no cash value</strong>, cannot be redeemed for money, and cannot be transferred between accounts.</li>
        <li>Unused coins are forfeited when your account is deleted, terminated, or inactive for more than 12 months.</li>
        <li>We may revoke coins obtained through fraud, chargeback, error, or in violation of these Terms.</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Refunds.</strong></p>
      <p>
        All purchases are final. Refund requests are handled by the
        Platform under its own policy:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Apple: <a href="https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204084" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reportaproblem.apple.com</a></li>
        <li>Google Play: <a href="https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/2479637" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Play refund policy</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>
